*   Updated `SummaryCard` and `getInsightTone` in [page.tsx](file:///home/ubuntu/Code/office/budget-tracker/agency/app/(dashboard)/ai-analytics/page.tsx) to use the dark theme's surface color (`dark:bg-[#161922]`) and subtle borders rather than saturated backgrounds in dark mode.

### 3. **Login & Resource Creation Latency (`BUG_003`)**
*   **Asynchronous Notifications:** Refactored `notifyTenantAdmins` and `notifyActorAndTenantOwners` inside [workspace-notifications.ts](file:///home/ubuntu/Code/office/budget-tracker/agency/lib/workspace-notifications.ts) to run notification insertions in a non-blocking background task.
