### 4. **Settings Toggle Knob Visibility (`BUG_005`)**
*   Overrode the toggle switch knob inside [settings-page-client.tsx](file:///home/ubuntu/Code/office/budget-tracker/agency/components/settings-page-client.tsx) using inline styles to prevent utility classes from overriding the knob color to the dark card background in dark mode, ensuring it stays visible.

